show.description: After her boyfriend Neil’s betrayal, Flora seeks revenge by impulsively marrying his enigmatic elder relative, Vittorio. But Vittorio is no ordinary man — he’s a vampire with a dark past and a secret obsession. In his study, Flora finds a photo of a woman who looks exactly like her… taken eighty years ago.
